  "title": "F&B Service Crew (SG/PR/WP all welcomed!)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Tengah, Singapore</p><p><strong>About the Role: </strong>We're a soymilk and waffle store looking for friendly, energetic crew members to join our team! You'll be the face of our store, serving customers and ensuring they have a great experience.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and serve soymilk beverages and waffles to customers</li><li>Handle cashier duties and process payments accurately</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of the store</li><li>Restock supplies and ingredients as needed</li><li>Provide friendly customer service and handle enquiries</li><li>Assist with store opening/closing duties</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>No experience required – training provided</li><li>Positive attitude and willingness to learn</li><li>Comfortable standing for extended periods</li><li>Available to work weekends and public holidays</li><li>Basic English communication skills</li></ul>",
